CMS PACKAGES
Oishii:		Web Application core.
    Oishii contains the libraries needed to create the Web application. It gives responsibility to handle the content to the appropriate packages for more specific output handling.

Bento:		Theme templating; Media Output.
    Bento deals with the display aspect of applications, and handles all templates and themes. Allows for easy switching in/out of page design modules.

Origami:	Formatting for input/output of Strings.
	Checks PHP settings, character encoding and html entities to ensure proper output for user.

## Outside Packages - temporary or not ##
Smarty - Templating
Zend - Framework